data.description: Amazing Single Story Home Located in the Picturesque area of Mentone referred to as "The Zanja" and in the Redlands School District.  Attention to Detail is evident inside and outside. From the Hardwood Floors to the Crown Molding.  The Kitchen features a perfect blend of Old World Charm to 1950's Character.  The Master Suite is a dream come True....Large Sitting area with Wood Cased Entrance to the Bedroom with Hardwood Floors, Walk-in Closet and Master Bath with upgraded vanity, counter-top and flooring. Main Bath has Beautiful Fixtures and Tile work throughout. Bedroom #2 has Hardwood Floors and 2 Windows for lots of light. The 3rd Bedroom/office with a One-of-a-Kind Penny Floor. Living room with Hardwood Floors. Enjoy the Nature of the area with the Greenspot Pumpkin Farm and the Mentone River Rocks.
